e_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Massey\" title=\"House Massey\">House Massey</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_before_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_2_Before_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years before Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">2&#160;BC</a>&#160;– <a href=\"/index.php/42_AC\" title=\"42 AC\">42&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table> \n<p><b>Triston Massey</b> was the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Stonedance\" title=\"Stonedance\">Stonedance</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Massey\" title=\"House Massey\">House Massey</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_Conquest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"War of Conquest\">War of Conquest</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Triston_Massey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon the Conqueror</a> prepared to begin his <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">conquest</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>, he summoned his friends and <a href=\"/index.php/Bannermen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bannermen\">bannermen</a> to attend to him on <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>, Lord Massey among them. Despite being sworn to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>, Triston had closer ties to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After Aegon was crowned as <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_All_Westeros\" title=\"King of All Westeros\">King of All Westeros</a>, he created the first <a href=\"/index.php/Small_council\" title=\"Small council\">small council</a> and Lord Triston had the honor of becoming <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_laws\" title=\"Master of laws\">master of laws</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Triston_Massey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.5</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\">1.6</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\">1.7</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Reign of the Dragons: The Conquest.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Aegon's Conquest.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Last known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Josua_Massey\" title=\"Josua Massey\">Josua Massey</a> </b><br /><small><i><b>as king </b></i></small>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Stonedance\" title=\"Lord of Stonedance\">Lord of Stonedance</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Ne